{"tid":959004,"cid":11,"subCid":0,"title":"Black Mirror: Bandersnatch 討論區","createTime":"2018-12-28T09:08:29.000Z","updateTime":"2018-12-29T05:58:55.000Z","uid":115539,"like":5,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"117a42121ac5a38aed6d25af03290b20e05e658e","tid":959004,"uid":115539,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-28T09:08:29.000Z","msg":"Black Mirror: Bandersnatch | Official Trailer [HD] | Netflix<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=IDwfL5vmIZA\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DIDwfL5vmIZA&d=HyHbeLBSYBMh6yY%2BD52dr10Hwm5JNK6yt%2FgZtp%2B4HOw%3D&h=7d96502a\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=IDwfL5vmIZA</a><br />\n<br />\n《黑鏡：潘達斯奈基》1984 年，一位年輕的程式設計師將一部情節複雜的奇幻小說改編成電玩，也因此開始質疑現實，眼前的挑戰使他心力交瘁。<br />\n<br />\n呢部係互動式電影，可以自行選擇故事的支線走向，<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">有主要5個唔同結局</span></strong>。<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"02c93d99fad88f54276cb4ce8dab37bb5cace0aa","tid":959004,"uid":48631,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-28T16:59:25.000Z","msg":"屌啦星我真係睇到火都黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d9e7de80408ea0c789556903e09425d8c25ba8fe","tid":959004,"uid":22839,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-28T17:15:06.000Z","msg":"打破第四面牆好夾今次互動劇情<br />\n但可惜故事唔知做乜尻<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"37bf14db27da0e54d0f143d86d9351c503d6d802","tid":959004,"uid":165808,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-28T20:54:24.000Z","msg":"我睇左幾個結局<br />\n<br />\n1. 主角死<br />\n2. 主角殺左老豆比人捉<br />\n3. 重新開發隻Game<br />\n<br />\n應該係有good ending, 不過出左近主角死左果個結局之後就唔比我再番轉頭揀其他支線<br />\n<br />\n我最想知入電話果道如果入岩左之後會點，因為我亂入電話😂"},{"pid":"3d9739f1541876a5ef3f266fe6dee76945c805b1","tid":959004,"uid":67041,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"quote":{"pid":"37bf14db27da0e54d0f143d86d935